🗂️ Voter Relationship Manager (VRM)

Nearnay’s Voter Relationship Manager gives you the power to build, organize, and personalize your entire voter base — from raw electoral rolls to dynamic supporter profiles — all in one place.

Smart Voter Import: Upload CSV/XLSX voter lists and map data fields effortlessly

Deduplication Engine: Detect and merge duplicate entries using AI-powered matching

Profile Builder: Maintain individual voter records with history, notes, touchpoints, and survey responses

Advanced Search &Filters: Quickly segment voters by booth, tag, location, or past engagement

Frequently Asked Questions

Is Nearnay easy to set up and use?

Yes. Nearnay offers guided onboarding, an intuitive dashboard, and mobile-friendly tools so even first-time users can get started quickly.

Can I upload my own voter list into Nearnay?

Yes. You can import voter data via CSV or Excel, and the platform will automatically clean, tag, and structure the information for use.

Can volunteers use Nearnay on their phones?

Definitely. Volunteers can access canvassing tools, submit reports, and view assigned tasks via the mobile-optimized version of Nearnay.

Does Nearnay work for both small and large campaigns?

Yes. Whether you're running for a municipal seat or a national office, Nearnay scales with your team size, data volume, and operational needs.
